title: Test
summary: This grouped bar chart has 5 categories of Product Name on the x axis representing 6 groups: 2013, 2014, 2015, 2016, 2017, and 2018.
Averaging these 6 groups, the highest category is found for Product Name Revlimid (cancer) with a mean value of 6651.17.
Followed by Pomalyst/Imnovid (cancer) with a mean value of 1155.52.
The lowest category is observed at Other that has a mean value of 295.17
showing a difference of 183.0% with the maximum value.

In case of Revlimid (cancer), 2013 shows more dominance than any other Product Name and it has the lowest value in Otezla (psoriasis). On the other hand, group 2014 is the second impactful group in this chart, and it's highest in case of Revlimid (cancer) and has the minimum dominance for Product Name Other.
